data.description: Welcome to your future home! This spacious gem awaits your personal touch to transform it into the home of your dreams. Featuring 3 beds and 3 baths, this large abode boasts a double-story living space that radiates comfort and warmth with 2 floor to ceiling fireplaces. The expansive wraparound deck is perfect for entertaining or enjoying peaceful evenings outdoors. Dive into relaxation with a brand-new, half above-ground pool, offering a refreshing escape during warmer months. Whole house automatic generator conveniently installed easing the mind during the winter months. Seize the opportunity to add your personal style to this canvas, and unlock the full potential of this incredible property. Your dream home is just around the corner   don't miss out on this exciting opportunity!
